						               													<description>This is an expansion that totally modifies the mechanics of the original game and the political economic conception of the classic Estanciero game. This expansion cannot be played without a copy of the base game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each player starts from the base of a sum of values &amp;#226;&amp;#128;&amp;#139;&amp;#226;&amp;#128;&amp;#139;together with an initial Field Deed. Gradually more Deeds of Fields, Chacras and Estancias are acquired, with which they are collected, rents are paid and grains or hacienda can be produced.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Railroads and Companies are bought and profits are collected. Seeds for planting or reproducers for the farm are purchased and the sales of what is produced are collected. Upgrades are purchased and penalties are paid. Taxes are paid for a Solidarity Fund intended for those players who go bankrupt to be able to resume the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game takes place over 4 years of 6 game turns per year.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game ends when the last player finishes playing the last turn of his fourth year or when there are no more players left who have yet to liquidate their hacienda or their harvest.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;OBJECTIVE OF THE GAME&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Be the player with the most wealth at the end of the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
